{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WheelEvent()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/WheelEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UI_Events\">UI Events</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>WheelEvent()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaMode\"><code>deltaMode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaX\"><code>deltaX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaY\"><code>deltaY</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaZ\"><code>deltaZ</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for UI Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CompositionEvent\"><code>CompositionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FocusEvent\"><code>FocusEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/InputEvent\"><code>InputEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyboardEvent\"><code>KeyboardEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseScrollEvent\"><code>MouseScrollEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MutationEvent\"><code>MutationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>WheelEvent()</code></strong> constructor returns a new <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent</code></a> object.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>Note:</strong> If you construct a synthetic event using this constructor, that event will not be <em>trusted</em>, for security reasons.\n    Only browser-generated <code>WheelEvent</code> objects are trusted and only trusted events trigger default actions.\n  </p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">new WheelEvent(type)\nnew WheelEvent(type, options)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"type\"><code>type</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A string with the name of the event.\n      It is case-sensitive and browsers always set it to <code>wheel</code>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"options\"><code>options</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An object that, <em>in addition of the properties defined in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/MouseEvent\" title=\"MouseEvent()\"><code>MouseEvent()</code></a></em>, can have the following properties:</p>\n    <dl>\n      <dt id=\"deltax\"><code>deltaX</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n      <dd>\n        <p>\n          A floating number representing the horizontal scroll amount in the <code>deltaMode</code> unit.\n          It defaults to <code>0.0</code>.\n        </p>\n      </dd>\n      <dt id=\"deltay\"><code>deltaY</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n      <dd>\n        <p>\n          A floating number representing the vertical scroll amount in the <code>deltaMode</code> unit.\n          It defaults to <code>0.0</code>.\n        </p>\n      </dd>\n      <dt id=\"deltaz\"><code>deltaZ</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n      <dd>\n        <p>\n          A floating number representing the scroll amount for the z-axis scroll amount in the <code>deltaMode</code> unit.\n          It defaults to <code>0.0</code>.\n        </p>\n      </dd>\n      <dt id=\"deltamode\"><code>deltaMode</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n      <dd>\n        <p>An integer representing the unit of the delta values scroll amount. It defaults to <code>0x00</code>. Permitted values are:</p>\n        <table>\n          <thead>\n            <tr>\n              <th>Constant</th>\n              <th>Value</th>\n              <th>Description</th>\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody>\n            <tr>\n              <td><code>DOM_DELTA_PIXEL</code></td>\n              <td><code>0x00</code></td>\n              <td>The delta values are specified in pixels.</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td><code>DOM_DELTA_LINE</code></td>\n              <td><code>0x01</code></td>\n              <td>The delta values are specified in lines.</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td><code>DOM_DELTA_PAGE</code></td>\n              <td><code>0x02</code></td>\n              <td>The delta values are specified in pages.</td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A new <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent</code></a> object.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#dom-wheelevent-wheelevent","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.WheelEvent.WheelEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.WheelEvent.WheelEvent","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/WheelEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent</code></a> interface it belongs to.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The WheelEvent() constructor returns a new WheelEvent object.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-09-13T06:51:25.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/wheelevent/wheelevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/wheelevent/wheelevent/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/c575deb5f1775b532360c612a85b35a5ff9525d9","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent","title":"WheelEvent"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/WheelEvent","title":"WheelEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"WheelEvent() - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}